{"comments":"OKLAB - Modern perceptually uniform color space.\n\n**BETTER THAN LAB:**\nOKLAB (2020, Björn Ottosson) improves on CIE LAB with:\n- More uniform hue perception\n- Better behavior for blue colors\n- Simpler math (no cube roots)\n- Faster computation\n- Better for gradient interpolation\n\n**Components:**\n- **L**: Lightness, 0.0 (black) to 1.0 (white)\n- **a**: Green-Red axis, typically -0.4 to +0.4\n- **b**: Blue-Yellow axis, typically -0.4 to +0.4\n\n**Use cases:**\n- Smooth color gradients (better than HSL or LAB)\n- Perceptually uniform color palettes\n- Color difference calculations\n- Modern CSS (oklch() function support)\n\n**Reference:**\nhttps://bottosson.github.io/posts/oklab/\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/OKLAB.purs","start":[134,1]},"title":"eqOKLAB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/OKLAB.purs","start":[135,1]},"title":"ordOKLAB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,123],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/OKLAB.purs","start":[137,1]},"title":